#: ../../../system/nitro.rst:55
msgid ""
"Enable debug mode. When enabled, the Nitro Hypervisor exposes the enclave's "
"serial console output via a vsock port that the machine model automatically "
"connects to. In debug mode, PCR values are zero. Default is ``off``."
msgstr ""

